replies.body:
Step 1: Play {{champion:17}} 
Step 2: Buy (or have a teammate buy) {{item:3512}} 
Step 3: Wait until {{champion:202}} comes to kill {{item:3512}} 
Step 4: Wait until {{champion:202}} is reloading
Step 5: Repeatedly auto attack {{champion:202}} while he's reloading
Step 6: As {{champion:202}} finishes reloading, blind him for an additional 2.5 seconds where he can't attack
Step 7: Collect your gold.
